{"tid":2501492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【傳真社】國安教育日紀律部隊學校開放參觀    過半入場為家屬及相關團體","createTime":"2021-04-23T11:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T11:47:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8337f874a3ae32c002003a13b9f50bc57c31d53d","tid":2501492,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T11:47:16.000Z","msg":"上周四是「全民國家安全教育日」，政府除了透過電視及戶外廣告等大肆宣傳，亦在多區舉辦展覽及活動，包括各紀律部隊訓練學校開放日，公眾事前可網上登記抽籤領取開放日門票，但當局未有公布名額。FactWire傳真社發現，當日5間訓練學校共約2,600人進場，但經網上抽籤獲得門票的公眾人士不足一半，其餘入場人士為各紀律部隊人員的家屬及相關團體成員。另外，5間訓練學校以警察學院的入場人數最多，超過其餘4間學校入場人數總和。政府拒絕回應相關原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/177988227_1722424054631308_8494077651662802112_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=973b4a&amp;_nc_ohc=SBoNJOMvmRUAX_J18u1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=e7a6d2fe4bfa095f5850f3cd27058da6&amp;oe=60A76650\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.6435-9%2F177988227_1722424054631308_8494077651662802112_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D973b4a%26_nc_ohc%3DSBoNJOMvmRUAX_J18u1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3De7a6d2fe4bfa095f5850f3cd27058da6%26oe%3D60A76650&h=961fbdfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n足本報道：<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/investigation/國安教育日紀律部隊學校開放參觀-過半入場為家屬/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Finvestigation%2F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E6%97%A5%E7%B4%80%E5%BE%8B%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E5%8F%83%E8%A7%80-%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%8A%E5%85%A5%E5%A0%B4%E7%82%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzktrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=12f14baa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/investigation/國安教育日紀律部隊學校開放參觀-過半入場為家屬/</a>"}]}